Then compare against existing construction SPP:

```sql
SELECT W.ECMS_PROJECT_NUM,
       W.WO_AUTH_NUM,
       W.CL_LINE_NUM,
       W.SPECIAL_PROV_NUM,
       W.SPECIAL_PROV_REV
FROM WORK_AUTH_SP W
WHERE W.ECMS_PROJECT_NUM = 91768
